**/node_modules

# Python virtual environments
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc

# IDE files
.vscode
.idea
*.swp
*.swo

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Documentation
README.md

# Build artifacts
**/build
**/.svelte-kit